{"pageProps":{"metadata":{"title":"Flet-後期","curriculumId":"1632297f-7a72-80a0-bd39-defe56830cdf","category":"後期","visibility":["基礎班","発展班"],"tags":["基礎班","Python","Flet","GUI"],"is_basic_curriculum":true,"id":"12"},"mdBlocks":[{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81dd-ad6a-c8a97d169502","parent":"Fletの要素であるコントロールは自分でカスタムすることが可能です。今回は「カスタムコントロール」を紹介します。","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81ec-9401-e5c89d504e76","type":"heading_2","parent":"## カストムコントロールとは","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8153-af41-f52257e1c45c","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8129-8221-ee9b72b9dcc9","parent":"カスタムコントロールは、Fletにあるコントロールのクラスを継承した新たなクラスを作り、親クラスの属性の値をカスタムしたコントロールです。（クラスの継承については「[**クラスの継承**](/posts/curriculums/16c2297f-7a72-803f-872e-ef1fab8e273e/16c2297f-7a72-80aa-8f18-cca16f8b3361)」をご覧ください）","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81a1-9793-f1854426f09b","parent":"例えば、見た目を変更した文字を使い回したいとします。文字を表示するには`Text`コントロールを使いますが、その見た目を変更するには`style`属性を設定しなければいけませんね。","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8175-8a5d-fb8d66eef1c3","type":"code","parent":"```python\nft.Text(\"文字\", style=ft.TextStyle(size=20))\n```","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81de-aac1-e2dfd9843243","parent":"`Text`コントロールの`style`属性の値を何度も書くのは面倒です。`style`属性の値が事前に決まっていれば書く必要はなくなります。それを可能にするのがカスタムコントロールです。","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8132-aa94-f9a386475597","type":"heading_2","parent":"## カストムコントロールを作る","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8130-82c2-c5079c6f52f7","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8121-9564-e2f93b6a125d","parent":"それでは、カスタムコントロールを作ってみましょう。","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-814e-8371-d190ceccd231","parent":"試しに、以下の設定のカスタムコントロールを作ってみましょう。","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8184-bc18-d6ce6ffa5bb8","type":"code","parent":"```python\nft.Text(\"文字\", style=ft.TextStyle(size=20))\n```","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81ac-a51d-f3fd34775c32","type":"callout","parent":"> カスタムコントロールを作る  \n> ```python  \n> import flet as ft  \n>   \n> class CustomText(ft.Text):  \n> \tdef __init__(self,value):  \n> \t\tsuper().__init__(value=value, style=ft.TextStyle(size=20)  \n> ```","children":[{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-814c-b28c-fb418d2b5dd9","type":"code","parent":"```python\nimport flet as ft\n\nclass CustomText(ft.Text):\n\tdef __init__(self,value):\n\t\tsuper().__init__(value=value, style=ft.TextStyle(size=20)\n```","children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81af-9c6d-f6d7474ea90f","parent":"ここでは`CustomText`というカスタムコントロールを定義しました。","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8105-a9cf-dc7f0ab3eeb6","parent":"`CustomText`は、`Text`コントロールをカスタムしたコントロールであり、最初から`style`が設定されています。","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81f4-a7e8-ff694502ed92","parent":"さっそく`CustomText`を使ってみましょう。","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81fb-8776-da1183ace581","type":"callout","parent":"> `CustomText`を使う  \n> ```python  \n> import flet as ft  \n>   \n> class CustomText(ft.Text):  \n> \tdef __init__(self,value):  \n> \t\tsuper().__init__(value=value, style=ft.TextStyle(size=20))  \n> \t\t  \n> def main(page: ft.Page):  \n>   \n> \tnormalText = ft.Text(value=\"普通のTextコントロール\")  \n> \tcustomText = CustomText(value=\"カスタムしたTextコントロール\")  \n>   \n> \tpage.add(normalText, customText)  \n>   \n> ```","children":[{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8164-8a23-c0632916c5d1","type":"code","parent":"```python\nimport flet as ft\n\nclass CustomText(ft.Text):\n\tdef __init__(self,value):\n\t\tsuper().__init__(value=value, style=ft.TextStyle(size=20))\n\t\t\ndef main(page: ft.Page):\n\n\tnormalText = ft.Text(value=\"普通のTextコントロール\")\n\tcustomText = CustomText(value=\"カスタムしたTextコントロール\")\n\n\tpage.add(normalText, customText)\n\n```","children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81b1-9c97-cc027043fe95","parent":"これを実行すると以下のような出力結果になります。","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81a4-8d34-e7a64d4413df","type":"callout","parent":"> 実行結果  \n> ![%E3%82%B9%E3%82%AF%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A7%E3%83%83%E3%83%88_2024-11-21_13.46.28.png](https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f9e367dd-1db7-428f-a2ed-c68a46952d5a/ce1253ca-6af5-47b3-b0a5-6a39a865800c/%E3%82%B9%E3%82%AF%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A7%E3%83%83%E3%83%88_2024-11-21_13.46.28.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466UVPCL2EK%2F20250304%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&X-Amz-Date=20250304T064048Z&X-Amz-Expires=3600&X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEK7%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIBH9ibp2uPE72HbXed4XDItum5nfWLAczn4Cd5kR7gDnAiEA72dmhAK2lKqGUcnKHP6vqtgUbNgTITpI4K473c3tcacqiAQI5%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FARAAGgw2Mzc0MjMxODM4MDUiDD2lacz5vrfYqxzZ7SrcA2Pt71C9n7d2NoATpwJSBKvuKROxJEgkvJoLYSKEh633%2BdxrKUyk%2FAhVgwTbIT0gjWKfGCilMmgzJYxzKXrxEBD%2BAVUtoE6N4t0BZPge2LAIvrCn4gDcbZ9aYUyOlrmIRlTGzrFbkS6xjuk0CwEShKCy8LoB%2F0J4%2Beiu83mmRq7Hft9pmD5dg%2FvT2d24VniZ7W4cqjgLvBqfqnkTPdp6dn09bbEwTh7%2BXb3uivChE7K%2B65CaH6uA49pDDpJrK7C0bCM%2FiwWl7WTNEmlDy51HPeVXEvGHD3eNwIc87MESphWwCCIiX2fgc4FdcKK75BrrwrzzcLseqSo%2B0bdcqRii%2FCHR%2FfPrSXKUhTEwtK7XX7X494OXy1oZXyY%2BvMggVOgkmpOF5wYXOUiaYg39lWgU97%2F%2FWSZPFR9nJ7EMZTs8J8JD%2Bz7bxESz4ozfI14qMmo%2FnuFcnPqcFoch0rwByOQVpdSQ4Sjq0VZTMYDBKtuynNUHAk3iwWpH020Afacyh5mpCFGyQz9m3%2FndNo7RARvAEKtWQJtTBMFQb8pCBOmQCiucE%2BwYj57%2BVJpsNSlxcsXLnP262nYzurGadH3l4sotALpuV9bPHPznJdnIh81sroRNFhs%2FN%2F6tX3I%2Bt%2FBDMNmdmr4GOqUBwArle12ysYdn5geuWY8%2F6Q5nNdO3q5SIs3bIEb%2B4eDObUWO3fgYVvx%2FEqZUcjcDHgwPyDb7DWnbLC4pHtOiFYpczA6m%2F2wmcJnV4S7UiRfDKeqvub7X6zMZTKJA%2F4dcyoi26bQb74P93Dbq6OLnS2lxMm0Lv1hUYrbgnosd%2FvvDYBUxS%2F4S2lyY%2FNpTeZoe95Hrx72QyjZxcPhVLHdviZ1hY8I5Y&X-Amz-Signature=3c8a52882deb931f99241eb739641781eb5e2362c6c414603f681eb5c55c128a&X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&x-id=GetObject)","children":[{"blockId":"19d